snippet.title: NSMB2 WillyMaker's Level Pack | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's a simple little hack that I've been working on last year but stopped working on it for a long time due to lack of motivation and problems with the final level, but now it's out!
Hope you like it!

Thanks to @hus_mighty and @Rimea for helping with some textures and information about modding this game.

Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/546255
(Tower includes a secret exit)

Logo by @B1_Gaming 
Bumpsy Plains remix by @Pokestir  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NO2P6ybFP6U

Thanks to my irl friends for testing this mod!

✪ Subscribe! www.youtube.com/channel/UCBDaY5sapkDhqlBBNJnW-Og?sub_confirmation=1

🔨 Super Mario Maker Mods: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmrgXrqSMR1an8mpt1yJVFnFxjs1l9btn&si=eqsxrn_tVQp8a6f-

🏁 Mario Kart 8 Deluxe Custom Tracks: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmrgXrqSMR1YtHvEAOAACz-CYsVZNqKYh&si=8bJ2fU75DQ0iKUh1
